    OVMSContainer -->|"uses for S3"| AWSSecret
    OVMSContainer -->|"uses for GCS"| GCPCreds
    OVMSContainer -->|"uses for Azure"| AzureCreds
    OVMSContainer -->|"uses for HF"| HFToken

